snippet.title: October gameplay preview
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay video to show the current progress of Unblocking. This is the PCVR version but the game will also be launched for Oculus Store in the end of this year.

In the meantime, you can play our Demo available at https://store.steampowered.com/app/1908260/Unblocking/ and https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/7856656291026503/

Website - https://unblockingvr.com/
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/unblockingvr
Twitter - https://twitter.com/UnblockingVR
Discord - https://discord.gg/5eSZefdtXs
Reddit - https://www.reddit.com/r/unblocking/
